---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services" description="E-commerce integration, API development, and data feed optimization services">
  <h1>Services</h1>
  
  <section class="intro">
    <p>
      I work with e-commerce companies to build reliable integrations, 
      optimize data pipelines, and solve the technical problems that 
      slow down operations.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="service-card featured">
    <div class="service-header">
      <h2>Data Feed Audit</h2>
      <span class="price">$500</span>
    </div>
    <p>
      A comprehensive review of your Shopify-to-Feedonomics (or similar) 
      data pipeline with actionable recommendations.
    </p>
    <h3>What's included:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Current feed health and error pattern analysis</li>
      <li>Field mapping review and optimization opportunities</li>
      <li>Performance bottleneck identification</li>
      <li>Prioritized fix recommendations with estimated impact</li>
      <li>30-minute walkthrough call</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="turnaround">Turnaround: 3-5 business days</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta">Get Started →</a>
  </section>

  <h2>Other Ways I Can Help</h2>

  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>Integration Development</h3>
      <p>
        Custom integrations between your e-commerce platform and third-party 
        services. Shopify, BigCommerce, WooCommerce, and more.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>API Development & Testing</h3>
      <p>
        Building robust APIs, creating comprehensive test suites, and 
        debugging existing integrations that aren't working as expected.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>Data Pipeline Optimization</h3>
      <p>
        Improving the reliability and performance of your data flows—from 
        product feeds to inventory sync to order management.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>Technical Consulting</h3>
      <p>
        Architecture reviews, vendor evaluations, and strategic guidance 
        for your e-commerce tech stack decisions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <p>Have a project in mind?</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta">Let's talk →</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .service-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .service-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-header h2 {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .price {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-card ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .turnaround {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    background: var(--text);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .service-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .service-item h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-item p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
